<dl id="n30172e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n30" href="#n30172e">N30 (VI.B.22)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n30all.htm#n30172e"> 172(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> drawn blood</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">The principle underlying the treatment <font color="green">[of]</font> all these cases <font color="green">[of sleeplessness]</font> is the same, namely, <mark>to induce some blood to leave</mark> the brain by causing a determination of it to another part of the body. <small> D. F. Fraser-Harris, <a name="FHMS" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#FHMS"><cite title="source">Morpheus, or: The Future of Sleep</cite></a> (1928) 47</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
